text: 2017, Palais Bourbon Jean Launay (born July 24, 1952) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Lot department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
